    <section id="id1170270251237">
      <title>Om ‘n wêreldkaart as ‘n groep te bestudeer om inligting te verkry</title>
      <para id="para-id1170270251237">
        <!--Empty sections are illegal in CNXML 0.5.  This empty paragraph is a place holder that was added as a byproduct of the word importer.-->
      </para>
